Update appsettings.json:

{
  "ConnectionStrings": {
    "DefaultConnection": "Server=tcp:cloudpossqlserver.database.windows.net,1433;Initial Catalog=CloudPOSDB;Persist Security Info=False;User ID=jerriadmin;Password=YourPassword123!;MultipleActiveResultSets=False;Encrypt=True;TrustServerCertificate=False;Connection Timeout=30;"
  }
}


Use Entity Framework Core to interact with the database:

dotnet add package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer
dotnet ef dbcontext scaffold "<your-connection-string>" Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer -o Models
